First write local code to fetch the PDF in a local test application.
It could be that you need to use java SE [**`HttpClient`**][1].

It just might be you need to fake a browser as agent, and accept cookies, follow a redirect. That all can be tested by a browser&#39;s development page looking at the network traffic in detail.

